The paper proposes a novel model for sequential recommendation using Recurrent Neural Networks (RNN) and focuses on modeling contextual information. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
